2026-05-15T06:51:01.2245652Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2246033Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2246227Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2246579Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2246915Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2247262Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2247587Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2247924Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2248487Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2248829Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2249120Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T06:51:01.2249282Z 32    -->
